Posh Pawn: At Christmas
Prestige Pawnbrokers' managing director James is struggling to get into the festive spirit, until a day out at the track with world superbike champion Carl Fogarty lifts his spirits and secures him a charity deal. Meanwhile, a former Miss England wants to trade in her diamonds for a new life in the United States, and Lawrence gets excited when a Falklands veteran turns up with a piece of Prince Charles and Princess Diana's 34-year-old wedding cake.
